{"tid":2032954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不如試吓放低黑衫？","createTime":"2020-05-24T10:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T12:16:20.000Z","uid":200063,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f3552745e15b7fe9776efc932a03895f8d9433","tid":2032954,"uid":200063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:53:14.000Z","msg":"由612開始，黑衫呢個dress code陪伴左我哋差唔多一年，甚至從單純既dress code演變成一種身份乃至精神標誌。但係運動過左咁耐，情況同大半年前大不相同，人海戰術已經難以再實行，時至今日，出去再着黑衫等於話晒比對面知邊個係目標。所以我覺得手足不妨放低黑衫呢個標誌，換作其他日常裝束，就算真係要散水都可以隨時變路人，大隱隱於市。以上只係個人愚見，如有犯駁，望各位屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e68933714797cc5fc4f67503959f6399d132612","tid":2032954,"uid":230146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"關衫撚事咩。<br />\n我接近三十，都係著黑衫，<br />\n速龍係我附近經過都冇事，<br />\n佢哋專蝦𡃁仔𡃁妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0bd2f986d580748cd7b2de698bb1db957bd9e8","tid":2032954,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:01:36.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但勇武呢 點解"},{"pid":"3025e523a67f39ecbcfd6591902209c4f0eba319","tid":2032954,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d0bd2f986d580748cd7b2de698bb1db957bd9e8","tid":2032954,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:01:36.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但勇武呢 點解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:01:47.000Z","msg":"點算"},{"pid":"fb69464b14ddf40a05e25852998a3559df1ca27e","tid":2032954,"uid":327204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:06:39.000Z","msg":"唔着黑衫 都會着深藍色既衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（樓下唔好on9幽默話藍衫係藍屍 thanks)"},{"pid":"ce998595177e2cee41d3135e2d6d83bd6c3bd5c7","tid":2032954,"uid":130901,"like":0